                <p class="slds-text-body--small slds-m-top--x-small">Looking to customize page layouts, add fields, or add users?  Try the <a href="/setup/forcecomHomepage.apexp?setupid=ForceCom" target="_blank">Salesforce Setup</a> pages.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="slds-media__figure slds-media__figure--reverse">
                <img src="{!URLFOR($Resource.CumulusStaticResources, '/Images/NPSP_Logo_Small_Cropped.png')}" class="img-rounded img-responsive" style="height: 75px" alt="NPSP Logo"/>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="slds-grid">
        <div class="slds-col--padded slds-size--4-of-12">
            <div class="slds-text-heading--medium slds-m-bottom--medium">
                Quick Starts
            </div>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://powerofus.force.com/SF_Getting_Started_Guide" target="_blank" >Getting Started Implementation Guide</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://powerofus.force.com/SF_Managing_Users_Guide" target="_blank" >Adding and Managing Users Quick Start</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://powerofus.force.com/SF_Importing_Data_Quick_Start" target="_blank" >Importing Data Quick Start</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="slds-col--padded slds-size--4-of-12">
            <div class="slds-text-heading--medium slds-m-bottom--medium">
                Power of Us Hub
            </div>
            <div class="slds-media slds-media--center">
                <div class="slds-media__figure">
                    <a href="https://powerofus.force.com/" title="Power of Us Hub" target="_blank"><img src="{!URLFOR($Resource.CumulusStaticResources, '/Images/hub-logo.png')}" alt="Power of Us Hub" /></a>
                </div>
                <div class="slds-media__body">
                    <p>Got questions? Got answers? Join the <a href="https://powerofus.force.com/HUB_System_Admin_Group" target="_blank">System Administrators</a> group in the <a href="https://powerofus.force.com/" title="Power of Us Hub" target="_blank">Power of Us Hub</a>!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slds-col--padded slds-size--4-of-12">
            <h3 class="slds-text-heading--medium slds-m-bottom--medium">
                Quick Links
            </h3>
            <div>
                <div class="slds-text-heading--small slds-m-bottom--small">
                    Documentation
                </div>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="https://powerofus.force.com/NPSP_Documentation" target="_blank" >NPSP 3.0 Documentation</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://powerofus.force.com/NPSP_Release_Notes" target="_blank" >NPSP 3.0 Release Notes</a></li>
                </ul>
